name: Tulip Red Silk Scarf
description:
Silk Scarves created from Jennifer Hopes new post graduate collection, Siamese Symmetry Streetwear. Designed by Jennifer Hope herself in from research into marine life. 

The scarves come in different sizes at different prices. 
The single sided scarves are brighter on one side than the other. The Double sided scarves are thicker and bright on both sides.
The Size of 70cm x 70cm would be perfect for a small head scarf or neck scarf or if your looking for something larger 100cm x 100cm is a better option. 

All scarves are printed on high quality fabric with original designs.

Silk Scarves may take longer to deliver than other items due to being made to order.
